<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 03:15:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美联储降息押注推动金价徘徊在一个月高位附近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-lingers-near-one-month-high-fed-rate-cut-bets-2024-07-08/</link><description>周一金价有所回落，但在前一交易日触及一个多月高点附近徘徊，因美国数据疲软提振了美联储 9 月降息的预期。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 03:01:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-lingers-near-one-month-high-fed-rate-cut-bets-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>债券需求强劲 中国央行调整流动性操作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-central-bank-tweaks-liquidity-operations-amid-strong-bond-demand-2024-07-08/</link><description>中国央行周一表示，将启动临时债券回购协议或逆回购协议，以提高公开市场操作效率，保持银行体系流动性充裕。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 02:59:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-central-bank-tweaks-liquidity-operations-amid-strong-bond-demand-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾与日本签署具有里程碑意义的防务协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-japan-sign-landmark-defence-deal-2024-07-08/</link><description>菲律宾总统通讯秘书切洛伊·加拉菲尔 (Cheloy Garafil) 周一在消息中表示，菲律宾和日本签署了一项协议，允许两国在对方领土上部署部队，这是两国安全关系在印太地区紧张局势不断升级的情况下的一个里程碑。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 02:51:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-japan-sign-landmark-defence-deal-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>欧元因法国民意调查僵局而有所缓解，美元在美国就业数据公布后疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/euro-eases-french-poll-gridlock-dollar-sluggish-after-us-payrolls-2024-07-08/</link><description>法国大选预测显示，由于左翼联盟出乎意料地强劲，法国大选将出现悬浮议会，欧元周一下跌，这给该国的财政前景带来了新的不确定性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 01:14:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/euro-eases-french-poll-gridlock-dollar-sluggish-after-us-payrolls-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市坚挺，欧元受法国政治僵局困扰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-08/</link><description>亚洲股市周一小幅走高，因投资者对美国 9 月降息信心增强，而法国大选表明议会将出现悬浮议会，欧元则面临政治不确定性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利总统欧尔班抵达中国执行乌克兰和平使命</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hungary-pm-orban-arrives-beijing-talks-with-chinese-president-xi-2024-07-07/</link><description>匈牙利总理欧尔班维克托周一抵达北京，此前他与俄罗斯总统普京就可能达成的乌克兰和平协议进行了会谈，此举激怒了一些欧盟领导人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 23:39:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hungary-pm-orban-arrives-beijing-talks-with-chinese-president-xi-2024-07-07/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜金与正指责韩国领导人利用紧张局势来分散政治注意力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-yo-jong-calls-south-korean-drills-provocation-kcna-says-2024-07-07/</link><description>官方媒体周一称，朝鲜领导人金正恩的妹妹金与正指责韩国总统尹淑烈在朝鲜半岛制造紧张局势，以转移人们对国内问题的注意力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 21:56:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-yo-jong-calls-south-korean-drills-provocation-kcna-says-2024-07-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：乐观情绪高涨，软着陆步入正轨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-07/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 21:49:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-07/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年温布尔登网球公开赛：第 8 天比赛顺序，德约科维奇和雷巴基纳在比赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/djokovic-rybakina-face-tricky-opponents-reach-wimbledon-last-eight-2024-07-07/</link><description>温网第四轮比赛将于周一在全英俱乐部结束。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 18:46:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/djokovic-rybakina-face-tricky-opponents-reach-wimbledon-last-eight-2024-07-07/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年温网：第 7 天阿尔卡拉斯、辛纳和拉杜卡努的比赛顺序</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/confident-alcaraz-faces-aggressive-humbert-wimbledons-fourth-round-2024-07-06/</link><description>温网比赛周日在全英俱乐部继续进行，世界顶尖选手将在伦敦争夺大满贯四分之一决赛的席位。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 20:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/confident-alcaraz-faces-aggressive-humbert-wimbledons-fourth-round-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>王在温网第三轮击败泪流满面的达特</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/wang-defeats-tearful-dart-wimbledon-third-round-2024-07-06/</link><description>周六，本土热门选手哈里特·达特在温布尔登网球公开赛上未能突破中国选手王新宇的防守，最终以 2-6 7-5 6-3 输掉了第三轮比赛，她在网前擦干了眼泪。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 16:41:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/wang-defeats-tearful-dart-wimbledon-third-round-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪收购泰国经销商Rever Automotive 20%股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-acquires-20-stake-thai-dealer-rever-automotive-2024-07-06/</link><description>周六，中国比亚迪公司表示，将收购泰国当地经销商 Rever Automotive 20% 的股份，泰国是比亚迪在中国以外最大的市场，比亚迪是电动汽车市场的领导者。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 14:21:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-acquires-20-stake-thai-dealer-rever-automotive-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>达赖喇嘛89岁了，流亡藏人担心没有他的未来</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/dalai-lama-turns-89-exiled-tibetans-fear-future-without-him-2024-07-06/</link><description>在印度北部雪山下的一座寺院里，受托保护达赖喇嘛并预言其人民未来的佛教僧人忧心忡忡。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 11:35:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/dalai-lama-turns-89-exiled-tibetans-fear-future-without-him-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车集团对欧盟反补贴关税“强烈不满”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-autos-group-strongly-dissatisfied-with-eu-anti-subsidy-tariffs-2024-07-06/</link><description>中国汽车工业协会（CAAM）在周六的一份声明中表示，该协会对欧盟提出的反补贴关税“强烈不满”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 11:34:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-autos-group-strongly-dissatisfied-with-eu-anti-subsidy-tariffs-2024-07-06/</guid></item><item><title>轩尼诗所有者路威酩轩集团表示，对中国干邑白兰地的调查是对欧盟汽车关税的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-cognac-probe-is-reaction-eu-car-tariffs-says-hennessy-owner-lvmh-2024-07-06/</link><description>轩尼诗干邑白兰地所有者路威酩轩集团 (LVMH) 财务主管周六表示，中国对欧洲干邑白兰地行业的反倾销调查是针对欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税的针锋相对的反应。</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jul 2024 10:42:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/china-cognac-probe-is-reaction-eu-car-tariffs-says-hennessy-owner-lvmh-2024-07-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>